opensmtpd-extras (5.7.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

    The opensmtpd-extras package has been split into two separate binary
    packages. Users wishing to continue using filters should install the
    opensmtpd-extras-experimental package. They are reminded that experimental
    filters may cause your OpenSMTPD installation to become unstable,
    insecure, or worse. Please proceed with caution!

